Syntax: learned

Displays all skills and spells that your character currently has access to,
along with your proficiency level in each. Skills you can use are filtered
from the full skill list based on your class and level.

The proficiency column shows how well-trained you are in each skill, ranging
from untrained to master levels. Higher proficiency means more reliable and
more effective use.

Output is shown in three columns for readability.

  learned         -- Shows all usable skills/spells and their proficiency.

For information about a specific skill, type:
  shelp <skill name>

See also: slist spells shelp train gain
